description.narrative: The Pacific Labour Mobility Annual Meeting (PLMAM) was established by the Labour Mobility Arrangement, which was signed alongside the PACER Plus Agreement. PLAMM is intended as a mechanism to advance Pacific labour mobility cooperation. This Activity supports the delivery of this important regional event during New Zealand's host year (2019) and in 2021.
